Package org.dockbox.selene.core.impl.files.annotations

  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    Default
    If a config entry is null or empty and is decorated with this, Neutrino will attempt to parse this value instead.
    DoNotGenerate
    Tells the Neutrino Object Mapper to not create this field at runtime if the default value is set.
    ProcessSetting
    Indicates that, when this annotation is present alongside a Setting annotation, some transformation of the node should occur at the following moments: before the value of the field is set from the ConfigurationNode after the value of the field is read from the ConfigurationNode, but just before it is written to the file
    RequiresProperty
    For any Setting decorated with this, it will only be updated if the Java property named in RequiresProperty.value() is set.
